text: "Doe Boy Fresh" is a 2007 song by American rap group Three 6 Mafia and American rapper Chamillionaire. The single was number 54 on the Billboard Hot 100. It reached RIAA gold certification status on July 27, 2007. ==Chart== Chart (2007) Peak position U.S. Billboard Hot 100 54 U.S. Billboard Hot R&B;/Hip-Hop Songs 74 U.S. Billboard Pop 100 60 ==Certifications== ==References== Category:2006 songs Category:Chamillionaire songs Category:Songs written by Chamillionaire
